            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_7774974854672543978.png",
                "id": "talent8494",
                "key": "迅烈倾霜拳",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "迅烈倾霜拳"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">寒烈的惩裁</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/d16aaeb6e3d7c751f1ac36d875668e80_2913641452814275274.png",
                "id": "talent70916",
                "key": "冰牙突驰",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰牙突驰"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">余威冰锥</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">本角色在本回合中受到伤害或治疗每累计到2次时：</span>此技能少花费1个元素骰（最多少花费2个）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/866bcc4723d1e09e478894bf4d1e70ef_4584060510538080023.png",
                "id": "talent92429",
                "key": "黑金狼噬",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "黑金狼噬"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">融化</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超导</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害<span>+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_7554331116564408423.png",
                "id": "talent29449",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">寒烈的惩裁</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色进行普通攻击时：</span>如果角色生命至少为6，则此技能少花费1个<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>，伤害+1，且对自身造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span>。</p><p>如果角色生命不多于5，则使此伤害+1，并且技能结算后治疗角色2点。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">余威冰锥</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方选择行动前：</span>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7051448748010762255.png",
